flowchart TB
    Query([Chat query]) --> Route{Current or explicit<br/>internet information needed?}
    Route -->|no| Local[Answer from local model and context]
    Route -->|yes| Normalize[Deterministic query normalization<br/>optional bounded image description]
    Normalize --> Privacy{OutboundPrivacyPolicy}
    Privacy -->|sensitive and cannot minimize| Block[Visible search-blocked event<br/>no network request]
    Privacy -->|safe minimized public query| MCP[MCP internet/search_web<br/>read-only stdio boundary]
    MCP --> Hybrid{Application-owned provider policy}

    Hybrid -->|ordinary query and key configured| Reserve{Reserve Google daily call<br/>default local cap 450}
    Reserve -->|budget available| ADK[Google ADK Agent<br/>Gemini 2.5 Flash, single turn<br/>include_contents none]
    Reserve -->|limit reached| Tavily
    ADK --> Grounding[Native google_search tool<br/>grounding metadata required]
    Grounding -->|attributable sources| GoogleResults[Google results<br/>nullable score]
    Grounding -->|failure, empty, or unattributed| Tavily[Tavily search<br/>scored results and relevance floor]
    Hybrid -->|Google disabled or failed| Tavily
    Hybrid -->|explicit verify or cross-check| Dual[Call each configured provider once]
    Dual --> ADK
    Dual --> Tavily

    Quota[(SQLite search quota<br/>provider, Pacific date, count only)] --> Reserve
    GoogleResults --> Merge[Bound, merge, URL-deduplicate<br/>retain provider provenance]
    Tavily --> Merge
    Merge --> MCPJSON[Compact MCP JSON<br/>provider plus bounded sources]
    MCPJSON --> Adapter[MCPWebSearchProvider<br/>local result validation]
    Adapter --> Prompt[Quoted untrusted prompt context]
    Adapter --> SSE[search and tool lifecycle SSE<br/>provider-attributed source cards]

    Isolation[Cloud worker receives only:<br/>minimized query<br/><br/>Never receives:<br/>user or conversation ID, history,<br/>personal memory, image bytes,<br/>MCP credentials or execution authority]
    ADK -. constrained by .-> Isolation

    Gemma[Local Gemma coordinator and final answer] --> Route
    Prompt --> Gemma

